videos.description: Frank Nutile tosses to Adonis Jennings who walks in for the 40-yard Temple touchdown.
videos.headline: Nutile finds Jennings for easy TD

videos.description: Frank Nutile lobs it up to Keith Kirkwood for his second passing touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Futile hits Kirkwood on fade for Temple score

videos.description: Temple head coach Geoff Collins likes how his offense has moved the ball with Frank Nutile under center.
videos.headline: Collins impressed with his QB in first half

videos.description: Frank Nutile completes the easy pitch-and-catch to extend Temple's lead.
videos.headline: Jennings hauls in his 2nd TD

videos.description: Navy finally finds the end zone with a reverse pass from WR Malcolm Perry to QB Zach Abey.
videos.headline: Navy uses trickeration for TD

videos.description: Adonis Jennings goes up to make the 33-yard grab to set up Temple at the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: Jennings' leaping grab leads to TD

videos.description: Delvon Randall lays out for the interception, adding insult to injury as Navy QB Zach Abey was hit hard on the play.
videos.headline: Randall makes diving pick

videos.description: Garret Lewis finds a wide open Brandon Colon in the back of the end zone for an easy score.
videos.headline: Navy backup QB Lewis throws 16-yard TD

videos.description: Garret Lewis rifles in a pass to Tyler Carmona for the Navy touchdown to cut the lead to 8.
videos.headline: Lewis fires a strike to Carmona

videos.description: Temple head coach Geoff Collins was proud of how his team fought and his QB Frank 'Juice' Nutile.
videos.headline: Collins hopes win can propel Temple to bowl eligibility

videos.description: Mike Golic Jr. was impressed with Temple's offense behind QB Frank Nutile, while Mike Golic Sr. thought Temple's defense stood out.
videos.headline: Golic and Golic Jr. break down Temple's convincing win
